					จังหวัด <div class="text-underline"  style="width:32%" >{{checkEmptyReturnDashed agreement.borrowerRegisteredAddress.province}}</div> โทรศัพท์ <div class="text-underline-left"  style="width:56%" >{{checkEmptyReturnDashed agreement.borrowerTelephone}}</div><span style="display: inline-block; width: 100%;"></span>
